draw((0,0)--A,dashed);
draw((0,0)--B,dashed);

dot("$-3 - 8i$", A, SW);
dot("$5 - 11i$", B, SE);
[/asy]

This means the image of $-3 - 8i$ is $(-3 - 8i)(1 + i) = \boxed{5 - 11i}.$

